              MOVE DFHGREEN TO TXT16C IN BANK35AO
              MOVE DFHGREEN TO TXT17C IN BANK35AO
              MOVE DFHGREEN TO TXT18C IN BANK35AO
              MOVE DFHGREEN TO RP1DAYC IN BANK35AO
              MOVE DFHGREEN TO RP1AMTC IN BANK35AO
