              MOVE DFHGREEN TO TXT19C IN BANK35AO
              MOVE DFHGREEN TO TXNPFKC IN BANK35AO
              MOVE DFHGREEN TO VERC IN BANK35AO
           END-IF.

           EXEC CICS SEND MAP('BANK35A')
                          MAPSET('MBANK35')
                          ERASE
                          FREEKB
           END-EXEC.
           GO TO SCREEN35-BUILD-AND-SEND-EXIT.

