      *****************************************************************
       CALL-DATECONV.
           MOVE BANK-ENV TO DD-ENV.
           MOVE 'UDATECNV' TO WS-DYNAMIC-PGM.
           CALL WS-DYNAMIC-PGM USING WS-TIME-DATE-WORK-AREA.
       CALL-DATECONV-EXIT.
           EXIT.

